  <h2>Smart Pot</h2>
  <div><img src="/assets/img/smart-pot.webp" alt="Smart Pot"></div>
  <p>The Smart Pot device is designed for automated plant care, monitoring soil moisture and adjusting irrigation as needed. Built on the Sensor Control Template.</p>

  <h3>Template</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/templates/sensor-control">Sensor Control</a>
  </ul>

  <h3>Key Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Soil moisture sensor embedded into the pot.</li>
    <li>Peristaltic pump embedded into the cartridge.</li>
    <li>Displays the current soil moisture reading.</li>
    <li>Buttons for sensor calibration and the irrigation threshold.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Use Cases</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Indoor Plant Care</li>
    <li>Automated Home Gardens</li>
  </ul>

