  <h2>Prototypes</h2>
  <h3>Prototype #2</h3>
  <p>Improvements:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Added buttons and display. This version no longer needs a computer attached to calibrate or configure the irrigation threshold.</li>
    <li>Swapped to a more durable waterproof sensor.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Issues:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The tubing from the pump into the pot is on the outside, when it should be hidden by the outter part of the pot. The design has since been flipped so this tube is hidden on the inside.</li>
    <li>The cartridge has a small gap in it. This has been fixed by filling in the top of the inner cartridge section and improving the fit.</li>
  </ul>
